TITLE: Episode 82 - Cutting Phootloose w/ The Pholosopher
DESCRIPTION: Maddie and Jessie have a social hour with one of the OG Internet Liberty Ladies, The PHOlosopher. They talk about the importance of self work and self care, as the ripple effects for a better world and society start with you, the individual, and how that is more vital than ever given the past year of trauma and tyrannical abuse.
